Description: chapelle_jewellery Visit our eBay Shop Add us to your Favourites list > Subscribe to our Newsletter > About Chapelle Delivery The Chapelle Guarantee Mens Rotary Les Originales automatic Burlington black leather strap watch GS90061/04 RRP £399.00 Now £269.00 Description Smart mens Rotary watch from the Les Originales Swiss made collection. The Burlington GS90061/04 Rotary watch features a black genuine leather textured strap and contrasting rose gold plated detailing. The rose gold plated casing houses the jet back round dial which has batons marking each hour and a date window at three o’clock. This automatic watch is powered by movement so never requires a battery. The elegant slim second’s hand sweeps around the dial which is finished with domed glass completing the vintage styling of the Les Originales collection. With a skeleton dial to the back of the watch, the intricate automatic mechanism, which contains 21 jewels can be seen working. This Rotary watch comes complete with a lifetime manufacturer’s warranty which covers the internal working parts. To maintain this warranty the watch is required to be serviced every 3 years ensuring it is kept at its best working condition.
